abstract: >
  A comparative ATAC-seq analysis workflow for identifying shared and differential
  chromatin accessibility patterns between Alzheimer's disease and Medulloblastoma
  microglia using BWA, SAMtools, MACS2, BEDTools, HOMER, DiffBind, and DESeq2.

license: MIT

repository-code: "https://github.com/AnkitaBhosale031/comparative-atac-seq-analysis"

keywords:
  - ATAC-seq
  - Bioinformatics
  - Epigenomics
  - Chromatin Accessibility
  - Alzheimer's Disease
  - Medulloblastoma
  - DiffBind
  - HOMER
